{"id":"808779991843241985","type":"text","timestamp":1771312705,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/808779991843241985","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://bunjywunjy.tumblr.com/post/807816843883675648/this-is-actually-hilarious-because-both-domestic\">bunjywunjy</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://blignick.tumblr.com/post/803440932374609920\">blignick</a>:</p><blockquote><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"634\" data-orig-width=\"854\" data-npf='{\"type\":\"video\",\"provider\":\"tumblr\",\"url\":\"https://va.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_t7j89hNYqb1zbh1kr.mp4\",\"media\":{\"url\":\"https://va.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_t7j89hNYqb1zbh1kr.mp4\",\"type\":\"video/mp4\",\"width\":854,\"height\":634},\"poster\":[{\"url\":\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_t7j89hNYqb1zbh1kr_frame1.jpg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"width\":854,\"height\":634}],\"filmstrip\":{\"url\":\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/previews/tumblr_t7j89hNYqb1zbh1kr_filmstrip.jpg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"width\":2000,\"height\":148}}'><video controls=\"controls\" autoplay=\"autoplay\" playsinline=\"playsinline\" muted=\"muted\" poster=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_t7j89hNYqb1zbh1kr_frame1.jpg\"><source src=\"https://va.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_t7j89hNYqb1zbh1kr.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"></source></video></figure></blockquote><p>this is actually HILARIOUS because both domestic rabbits and domestic cats practice dominance-related social grooming but for wildly different reasons.</p><p>if you&rsquo;re a rabbit, the boss rabbit is the one who gets groomed by its subordinate rabbits. </p><p>but if you&rsquo;re a cat&hellip; the boss cat is the one that grooms the other cats.</p><p>BOTH these idiots are going &ldquo;aw yeah, it&rsquo;s good to be on top &gt;:) &rdquo;</p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"blignick","active":true,"theme":{"header_full_width":720,"hea